  "text": "Step 1 is sequentially written into every column of the matrix in Equation [CITATION_1] . In this way, the submatrix (W im ) of the supermatrix is constructed. As shown in Equation (7), all clusters are arranged in numerical order. Then the elements in every cluster are placed vertically and horizontally on the left and top of the supermatrix, respectively. Finally, the submatrix (W im ) calculated by Equation (6) is filled into the corresponding position of the supermatrix (W p ). (W p ) is constructed with p as a control criterion.",
